<refsect1 id="gstreamer-GstDeviceProvider.description" role="desc">
<title role="desc.title">Description</title>
<para>A <link linkend="GstDeviceProvider"><type>GstDeviceProvider</type></link> subclass is provided by a plugin that handles devices
if there is a way to programatically list connected devices. It can also
optionally provide updates to the list of connected devices.</para>
<para>Each <link linkend="GstDeviceProvider"><type>GstDeviceProvider</type></link> subclass is a singleton, a plugin should
normally provide a single subclass for all devices.</para>
<para>Applications would normally use a <link linkend="GstDeviceMonitor"><type>GstDeviceMonitor</type></link> to monitor devices
from all relevant providers.</para>

</refsect1>
